  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/chapter-3/article-iv/section-sec.-3.53"
             temporalId="sSEC_ 3_53">
      <num>SEC. 3.53</num>
      <heading>Operative dates of article</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The provisions of this article shall be operative only during a sixty (60) calendar
               day period of time immediately preceding an election, as the term &quot;election&quot; is defined
               in Subsection (i) of Section 3.52 of this article.</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 39.78, 10/30/78.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
